{"tid":2201412,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［大腸癌］想曾經患有或現有既巴打入黎傾早期症狀","createTime":"2020-09-13T19:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T13:01:07.000Z","uid":128210,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f33e83f8f935226c4a4ece22953f34be02f67ff1","tid":2201412,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"想問下有無巴打現有或曾經患有 大腸癌。<br />\n想問下啲症狀係點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwUbNJq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwUbNJq.png&h=aa378a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1，第一點第二點都有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zThwNJv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzThwNJv.png&h=81fff3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2，就2/4點都有。<br />\n<br />\n最近排便都唔成形，同即使食好多菜，去完都仲想去咁，去咗都未去乾淨咁。本身筋膜炎有睇緊中醫，佢隨口答我氣虛咁虛下就完topic。<br />\n<br />\n想咁多位巴打幫下手，想知早期症狀係點。<br />\n唔好問我做咩唔照腸鏡⋯成皮野睇一次對普通打工仔真係好難拎出黎。如果早期病徵我中既話，會去照，但想有多少少把握先。<br />\n唔該晒。"},{"pid":"0f8c706dfb8ea4d8370b1bce34bf06dfc954132c","tid":2201412,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:08:01.000Z","msg":"同因為有肚腩，所以唔知小腹有無漲⋯"},{"pid":"4db0cc91099cde62089676f56e26474c89201eee","tid":2201412,"uid":98387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:09:27.000Z","msg":"教協照羅 便好多"},{"pid":"aa7aa554c19927913ef425df786f19061b27bd08","tid":2201412,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4db0cc91099cde62089676f56e26474c89201eee","tid":2201412,"uid":98387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:09:27.000Z","msg":"教協照羅 便好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:11:42.000Z","msg":"即刻去查，又幾平，$4000 。但駛唔駛要咩資格先去得教協照？"},{"pid":"6bbb0bbead9bc396d5a47aa5c69001a2d207038d","tid":2201412,"uid":98387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:16:07.000Z","msg":"係6千呀 2千係手術房費 如果你有息肉又貴d 唔洗架 普通市民都可以預約 我照過幾個月前無痛的"},{"pid":"84cce9b9559da97847697364b3d3176b53390b18","tid":